    "Answer": "With the introduction of the Staking Layer, Polygon becomes capable of supporting a practically unlimited number of Layer 2 chains, each fully programmable both on the application and the configuration level. This design fully delivers on the requirement of exponential scalability without sacrificing security and user experience."
